<p class="ql-align-center">驾驶员平时开车上路</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最怕什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怕堵车？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经习惯哒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多点耐心总能到家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怕碰瓷？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有行车记录仪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201214/4eecc73118274d7aa57059aef5b402c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为老司机平常开车最怕的莫过于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>违法扣分</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>12分很珍贵啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201214/79bdd605bccd4794931d870991ab45e5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
